replies.body:
I want some damn stats on those sight stones other than health

{{item:2049}} {{item:2045}} 

Don't gotta give 100 AP or something on a Sight stone, but hell, even 30 or 40 AP wouldn't be bad.

Yea right now it seems like supports are giving up so much for their utility, that people decide it's not worth it and just pick "Supports" so that they can keep their damage and waveclear without losing too much utility. The worst part is, it seems more and more like these guys end up doing better overall throughout the game.

{{champion:1}} {{champion:111}} {{champion:48}} {{champion:99}} {{champion:161}} {{champion:143}} {{champion:106}} {{champion:76}} 

True supports are in a pretty bad spot.
